---
title: One-Pan Smoky Pork Tacos with Green Pepper, Pickled Onion & Monterey Jack Cheese
description: These ground pork tacos taste slow-cooked, thanks to Southwest-style seasonings plus tomato paste for umami-packed richness, and savory onion and green pepper. It’s all stuffed into steamy tortillas with Monterey Jack cheese, pickled onion, tomato, and chipotle crema—basically, everything we crave on taco night and then some.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ba4be6fb4859096c8b62a5-154816ee.jpeg
